---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="How We 10x'd Revenue Without Changing the Offer or Spending a Dollar More on Ads — SalesAtScale.io"
  description="Scaled a tax strategy offer from ~$100K/month to $1M+ using the existing pipeline by fixing the conversion bottleneck."
>
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1000px] px-6 pt-28 pb-12 mx-auto">
    <a href="/#case-studies" class="font-chivo text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] hover:text-heading transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 w-fit" style="color:#94A3B8;">
      <span>&larr;</span> Back to Case Studies
    </a>
  </div>

  <header class="w-full max-w-[1000px] px-6 pb-12 mx-auto" style="border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(51,65,85,0.6);">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
      <span class="font-chivo font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs text-blue">Tax Strategy Consulting</span>
      <span style="color:#334155;">|</span>
      <span class="font-chivo font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-xs" style="color:#94A3B8;">2026</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="font-chivo font-black text-4xl md:text-[56px] leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-12" style="color:#F8FAFC;">
      How We 10x'd Revenue Without Changing the Offer or Spending a Dollar More on Ads
    </h1>
  </header>

  <main class="w-full max-w-[800px] px-6 py-16 mx-auto">
    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-16">
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background:#0D0D0D; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
        <div class="font-chivo text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-2" style="color:#64748B;">Book Rate</div>
        <div class="font-chivo text-4xl font-black" style="color:#F8FAFC;">28%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background:#0D0D0D; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
        <div class="font-chivo text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-2" style="color:#64748B;">Show Rate</div>
        <div class="font-chivo text-4xl font-black" style="color:#F8FAFC;">77%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background:#0D0D0D; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">
        <div class="font-chivo text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-2" style="color:#64748B;">Close %</div>
        <div class="font-chivo text-4xl font-black" style="color:#F8FAFC;">52%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-full h-px mb-12" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);"></div>

    <p class="font-chivo font-bold text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed mb-12" style="color:#94A3B8;">
      Scaled a tax strategy offer from ~$100K/month to $1M+ using the existing pipeline by fixing the conversion bottleneck.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 font-chivo font-medium text-[19px] leading-[1.8]" style="color:#94A3B8;">
      <p>The bottleneck wasn't lead flow; it was lead quality and follow-up cadence. We implemented a 5-minute speed-to-lead protocol and a pre-call homework sequence that pre-sold the prospect before they ever reached the calendar.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 p-12 rounded-[2rem] border shadow-2xl" style="background:#0D0D0D; border-color:rgba(0,59,224,0.2); box-shadow:0 25px 50px rgba(0,59,224,0.05);">
      <h4 class="font-chivo font-black text-3xl mb-4 uppercase tracking-tighter" style="color:#F8FAFC;">Ready to scale?</h4>
      <p class="font-chivo font-bold text-lg mb-8" style="color:#94A3B8;">Book a scale audit to find the hidden leverage points in your sales process.</p>
      <a href="/apply/" class="inline-block bg-blue hover:bg-blue-hover text-white font-chivo font-black py-5 px-10 rounded-2xl transition-all uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-xs shadow-btn-glow hover:shadow-btn-glow-hover">Book Scale Audit</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
